HALF-ORC
Ability Score Increase: STR +2, CON +1
Size: Medium
Speed: 30 feet
Darkvision
Menacing: Proficiency in Intimidation skill
Relentless Endurance: When reduced to 0 hit points but not killed outright, you can drop to 1 hit point instead. Once per long rest
Savage Attacks: If rolled critical hit with a melee weapon, you can roll one of the weapon's damage dice one additional time and add it to the extra damage of the critical hit
Languages: Common, Orc. 
